    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in really wonderful shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and consistently maintained, so it still runs like a dream. Whether you\u2019re just commuting to work or planning a fun weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to go. Come by, say hi, and take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
