      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, delivering power through a functional variable M differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal cam timing. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings, maintaining the sharp turn-in characteristics of the McPherson strut/multi-link setup. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains tight with no signs of rod bearing fatigue. A purist\u2019s spec for those prioritizing chassis dynamics and powertrain integrity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
