      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive shape. The exterior retains a deep luster, showing only the minor, superficial road wear consistent with a well-loved daily driver. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the upholstery is free of tears, and every button, dial, and digital display functions perfectly. Mechanically, it is robust and reliable, having benefited from regular oil changes and scheduled maintenance. It starts effortlessly, shifts smoothly, and provides a quiet, confident ride. This is a turn-key car that offers the perfect balance of performance and longevity for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
